qualitative vs quantitative research 

qualitative research is primarily exploratiory research. it is used to gain an understanding of underlying reasons
opinions and motivations. it provides insights into the problem or helps to develop ideas or hypothisize

quantitativ is used to quantify the problem by way of generating numerical data or data that can be transfromed into usable statistics. 
